/* ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
   RUNETERRA LEGENDS HUBS - ULTRA MODERN HEXTECH GLASS DESIGN SYSTEM
   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛ */

/* --- Variables & Core Palette --- */
:root {
  /* Hextech Gold Theme */
  --gold-dark: #785a28;
  --gold-medium: #c89b3c;
  --gold-light: #f0e6d2;
  --gold-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #785a28 0%, #c89b3c 50%, #f0e6d2 100%);

  /* Void / Cosmic Magic Dark Purple Palette */
  --bg-deep: #07040d;
  --bg-base: #0f0a1c;
  --bg-elevated: #161026;
  --bg-card: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.75);

  /* Accents & Status */
  --magic-blue: #00d2ff;
  --magic-cyan: #00bc8c;
  --magic-purple: #8e2de2;
  --error: #ff4e50;

  /* Borders & Glassmorphism */
  --border-light: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.2);
  --border-glow: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.45);
  --glass-bg: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4);
  --glass-blur: blur(14px);
  --shadow-glow: 0 0 12px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.5);
  --text-dim: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
  --text-faint: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.48);

  /* Fonts */
  --font-heading: 'Cinzel', serif;
  --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  --font-ui: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;

  /* Layout Depth */
  --z-bg: -3;
  --z-particles: -2;
  --z-nav: 100;
  --z-card: 10;
  --z-modal: 1000;
  --z-lightbox: 2000;
}

/* --- Resets & Base Styles --- */
*, *::before, *::after {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
  height: 100%;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  font-size: 15px;
  background-color: var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-color: var(--gold-medium) var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}

body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  color: #ffffff;
  /* Deep cosmic radial — violet core fading to pure void black, complemented
     by subtle gold/cobalt nebulae anchored to opposite corners. */
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(22, 16, 38, 1) 0%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 25% 0%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.12) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 90%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 90% 25%, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
  background-color: var(--bg-deep);
  line-height: 1.6;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

::selection {
  background: var(--gold-medium);
  color: #000;
}

/* Floating Scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: var(--bg-deep);
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: var(--gold-dark);
  border-radius: 5px;
  border: 2px solid var(--bg-deep);
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: var(--gold-medium);
}

/* Standard Premium Link */
a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}
a:hover {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

img {
  display: block;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

button {
  font-family: inherit;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: inherit;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* --- Particles Canvas & Deep Magic Backgrounds --- */
#particles {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  z-index: var(--z-particles);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.bg-gradient {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: 
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 15%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 85%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
  z-index: var(--z-bg);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.bg-grid {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: 
    linear-gradient(rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000000 40%, transparent 80%);
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000000 40%, transparent 80%);
  z-index: var(--z-bg);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* --- Header / Navbar --- */
.navbar {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 76px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 4rem;
  background: rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  z-index: var(--z-nav);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.navbar.scrolled {
  height: 64px;
  background: rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.9);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.nav-logo-mark {
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  animation: logoGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes logoGlow {
  from { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2px rgba(200,155,60,0.3)); }
  to { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(200,155,60,0.8)); }
}

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 3rem;
}

.nav-links a {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  padding: 0.4rem 0;
  position: relative;
}

.nav-links a::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 50%;
  width: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.nav-links a:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

.nav-links a:hover::after,
.nav-links a.active::after {
  width: 100%;
}

.nav-mobile-toggle {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  width: 30px;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  z-index: 101;
}

.nav-mobile-toggle span {
  display: block;
  height: 2px;
  width: 100%;
  background: var(--gold-light);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

/* --- Hero Section --- */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  /* Establish a stacking context so the splash sits above the global backgrounds,
     not behind the <html>/<body> gradient that was hiding it. */
  isolation: isolate;
}

.hero-splash {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center 25%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  /* Cinematic look: dreamy but visible — far less aggressively dimmed than before. */
  filter: brightness(0.62) saturate(1.05) contrast(1.05);
  transform: scale(1.12);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), transform 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  will-change: opacity, transform;
}

.hero-splash.loaded {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: scale(1);
  animation: slowZoom 60s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes slowZoom {
  from { transform: scale(1.04) translate(-0.6%, -0.8%); }
  to   { transform: scale(1.12) translate(0.6%, -1.4%); }
}

/* Color grading washes drawn over the splash so the hero keeps the mystical
   gold/violet identity while still letting the champion art read through. */
.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 0%,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.45) 40%,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.72) 72%,
    var(--bg-deep) 100%);
}

/* Cinematic edges — darkens corners for a faux-darkroom vignette and focuses
   the eye on the center where the title lives. */
.hero-vignette {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 42%, transparent 0%, transparent 38%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 82%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.9) 100%),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 0%, transparent 22%, transparent 78%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 100%);
}

/* Subtle gold/violet light sweep drifting across the hero text area */
.hero-overlay::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 18% 22%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 82% 78%, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.14) 0%, transparent 50%);
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Floating "Featured Champion" credit in the lower-right corner */
.hero-credit {
  position: absolute;
  right: 2rem;
  bottom: 2rem;
  z-index: 2;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(8px);
  transition: opacity 1s ease 0.4s, transform 1s ease 0.4s;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  pointer-events: none;
  max-width: min(40ch, 60vw);
  text-align: right;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.hero-credit::before {
  content: "✦";
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 0.5em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.hero-credit.visible {
  opacity: 0.78;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .hero-credit { font-size: 0.68rem; right: 1rem; bottom: 1rem; }
}

.hero-content {
  max-width: 860px;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 100px;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.6);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
}

.hero-badge-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--magic-cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--magic-cyan);
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--magic-cyan); }
  100% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7.5vw, 5.5rem);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
}

.hero-title-line {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 30%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}

.hero-title-amp {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  font-size: 0.48em;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 0.4rem 0;
}

.hero-divider {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin: 2.2rem 0;
  width: 100%;
}

.hero-divider-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-light) 50%, transparent);
}

.hero-divider-mark {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.hero-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-light);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  cursor: pointer;
}

.hero-cta:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.45), 0 0 15px var(--gold-light);
  color: #000000;
  background: #ffffff;
}

.hero-cta-arrow {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.hero-cta:hover .hero-cta-arrow {
  transform: translateY(4px);
}

/* Hero Stats Bar */
.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 3.5rem;
  margin-top: 4.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 3.5rem;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.75);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
  border-radius: 12px;
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
  z-index: 2;
}

.hero-stat {
  text-align: center;
}

.hero-stat-num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
}

.hero-stat-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  margin-top: 0.2rem;
}

.hero-stat-sep {
  display: block;
  width: 1px;
  height: 44px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--border-light) 50%, transparent);
}

/* Mouse Scroll Indicator */
.hero-scroll-hint {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 2rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  z-index: var(--scroll-hint-z);
}

.scroll-mouse {
  width: 24px;
  height: 38px;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--text-faint);
  border-radius: 20px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  padding-top: 6px;
}

.scroll-wheel {
  width: 4px;
  height: 8px;
  background: var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 4px;
  animation: scrollAnim 1.6s infinite ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes scrollAnim {
  0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
  100% { transform: translateY(14px); opacity: 0; }
}

/* --- Section Title --- */
.section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.section-title-line {
  display: block;
  width: 80px;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-medium) 50%, transparent);
}

/* --- Controls: Search & Filters --- */
.champions-header {
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}

.controls {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1.2rem;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.search-box {
  position: relative;
  flex: 1;
  max-width: 320px;
  min-width: 260px;
}

.search-icon {
  position: absolute;
  left: 1.2rem;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.search-box input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3.2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.8);
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 1rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.search-box input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
}

.search-box input::placeholder {
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* Pill tags filters */
.filter-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.filter-tag {
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.5);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.filter-tag:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  color: #ffffff;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.filter-tag.active {
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  border-color: var(--gold-light);
  font-weight: 700;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.3);
}

.result-count {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-top: 1rem;
  min-height: 1.5em;
}

/* --- Champions Grid & Cards --- */
.champions-section {
  padding: 5rem 4rem;
  max-width: 1600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: 2.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
}

/* Cards (Vertical Loading Format) */
.card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  height: 390px;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.card-img-wrapper {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 1;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), filter 0.6s ease;
  filter: saturate(0.9) brightness(0.85);
}

.card-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.1) 0%, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4) 40%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.95) 100%);
  z-index: 2;
  transition: background 0.4s ease;
}

.card-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 3;
  margin-top: auto;
  padding: 2rem 1.6rem 1.6rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.card-role {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.card-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #ffffff;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

.card-title {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

/* Interactive Card Footer Reveal */
.card-footer {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--magic-blue);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 1.2rem;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.card-footer-arrow {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

/* Card hover triggers */
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
}

.card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.08);
  filter: saturate(1.2) brightness(1.05);
}

.card:hover .card-overlay {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0) 0%, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.25) 30%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.98) 100%);
}

.card:hover .card-footer {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.card:hover .card-footer-arrow {
  transform: translateX(5px);
}

/* --- Loader Spinner --- */
.loader {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.loader-spinner {
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  border: 3px solid rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19) infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

.no-results {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
}

.no-results-icon {
  display: block;
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* --- Detailed Modal --- */
.modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: var(--z-modal);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  animation: modalFadeIn 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalFadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

.modal.fade-out {
  animation: modalFadeOut 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalFadeOut {
  from { opacity: 1; }
  to { opacity: 0; }
}

.modal-backdrop {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}

.modal-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1140px;
  max-height: 90vh;
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), inset 0 0 30px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.05);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  animation: modalSlideUp 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalSlideUp {
  from { transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.97); }
  to { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
}

/* Inner short load structure */
.modal-wrapper.min-load {
  max-width: 450px;
  height: auto;
  padding: 4rem;
}

/* Hextech close button — inherits all base styling from the shared
   .lightbox-btn/.lightbox-close/.modal-close-btn group below. */
.modal-close-btn {
  top: 1.5rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
}

/* Panoramic Header (Perfect sizing) */
.modal-header {
  position: relative;
  height: 280px;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center 20%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 2.5rem 3.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
}

.modal-header-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.2) 0%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.6) 50%, 
    var(--bg-elevated) 100%);
  z-index: 1;
}

.modal-header-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 2rem;
  width: 100%;
}

.modal-profile-img {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3.5px solid var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
  background: var(--bg-deep);
}

.modal-header-meta {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.modal-champ-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.modal-champ-title {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.modal-diff-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.meta-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* Custom Stellar difficulty rating */
.difficulty-stars {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  line-height: 1;
}

.difficulty-stars::before {
  content: "★★★★★";
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  clip-path: inset(0 calc(100% - (var(--diff) * 10%)) 0 0);
  -webkit-clip-path: inset(0 calc(100% - (var(--diff) * 10%)) 0 0);
}

.modal-badges {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.modal-tag-badge {
  background: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.15);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-medium);
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.8rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

/* --- Tabs Layout --- */
.modal-body {
  padding: 2.5rem 3.5rem 3.5rem;
}

.tabs-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
}

/* Premium Navigation header */
.tabs-header {
  display: flex;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--border-light);
  gap: 2.5rem;
}

.tab-btn {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  padding: 0.8rem 0;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.tab-btn span {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.tab-btn:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

.tab-btn.active {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.tab-btn::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1.5px;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 2.5px;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.tab-btn.active::after {
  transform: scaleX(1);
}

/* Panel management */
.tab-panel {
  display: none;
  animation: panelIn 0.4s ease forwards;
}

.tab-panel.active {
  display: block;
}

@keyframes panelIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* --- Lore Content --- */
.lore-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
}

.lore-text h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.lore-text p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  text-align: justify;
}

.champion-sidebar-info {
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.8rem;
}

.champion-sidebar-info h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
}

.stats-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.8rem;
}

.stats-list li {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.stats-list li span {
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

.stats-list li strong {
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

/* --- Combative Abilities --- */
.abilities-detail-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

.ability-detail-card {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.8rem;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.ability-detail-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.65);
}

.ability-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
}

.ability-img-wrap img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold-dark);
}

.ability-letter {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -6px;
  right: -6px;
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-medium);
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.ability-letter.passive {
  border-color: var(--magic-blue);
  color: var(--magic-blue);
}

.ability-desc-wrap {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  width: 100%;
}

.ability-desc-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.ability-desc-header h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.ability-meta-tags {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.meta-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.meta-tag.cost {
  background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.3);
  color: var(--magic-blue);
}

.meta-tag.cd {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  color: var(--text-dim);
}

.ability-description-txt {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.ability-tooltip {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* --- Skins Slider & Gallery (Uncropped / Clickable) --- */
.skins-tab-header {
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.skins-tab-header p {
  color: var(--text-faint);
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.modal-skins-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scrollbar-color: var(--gold-medium) var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}

/* Widescreen container for loading format portraits */
.modal-skin-card {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  width: 200px;
  cursor: pointer;
  perspective: 1000px;
}

.modal-skin-card-inner {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  height: 360px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.modal-skin-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.modal-skin-card-title {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1.5rem 1rem 1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.95) 80%);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--text);
  z-index: 3;
}

/* Zoom overlay */
.modal-skin-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.7);
  opacity: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  z-index: 2;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.zoom-icon {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  transform: scale(0.8);
  transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
}

.zoom-lbl {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--gold-light);
}

/* Hover skins */
.modal-skin-card:hover .modal-skin-card-inner {
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.3);
  transform: translateY(-6px);
}

.modal-skin-card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.modal-skin-card:hover .modal-skin-overlay {
  opacity: 1;
}

.modal-skin-card:hover .zoom-icon {
  transform: scale(1);
}

/* Skeletons */
.modal-skin-card.skeleton .modal-skin-card-inner {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bg-deep) 25%, var(--bg-elevated) 37%, var(--bg-deep) 63%);
  background-size: 400% 100%;
  animation: shimmer 1.4s infinite;
}

@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: 100% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -100% 0; }
}

/* --- Premium Widescreen Lightbox --- */
.lightbox-modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: var(--z-lightbox);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  animation: modalFadeIn 0.3s ease-out forwards;
}

.lightbox-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.96);
}

.lightbox-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 96vw;
  height: 92vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 2;
}

.lightbox-image-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  flex: 1;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  /* Leave breathing room at the bottom so the caption never overlaps the art */
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: visible;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
}

.lightbox-img {
  /* Use the whole wrapper — LoL splash arts are ultra-wide (~16:7), so we
     let width and height both stretch up to viewport while keeping aspect. */
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  max-height: 100%;
  object-fit: contain; /* Absolutely NO crop, full original artwork preserved */
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}

.lightbox-loader {
  position: absolute;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border: 3.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-top-color: var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 0.8s infinite linear;
}

/* Shared Hextech control button styling — lightbox & modal close */
.lightbox-btn,
.lightbox-close,
.modal-close-btn {
  position: absolute;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.55);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
  color: var(--gold-light);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease,
              transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.08);
  z-index: 10;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  line-height: 0;
  /* Critical: explicit transform-origin prevents baseline-shift bugs on hover in/out */
  transform-origin: 50% 50%;
}

.lightbox-btn svg,
.lightbox-close svg,
.modal-close-btn svg {
  width: 1.4em;
  height: 1.4em;
  display: block;
  margin: auto;
  /* Force exact pixel-perfect centering regardless of font metrics */
  position: relative;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.lightbox-btn:hover,
.lightbox-close:hover,
.modal-close-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-dark) 0%, var(--gold-medium) 60%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
  color: #07040d;
  border-color: var(--gold-light);
  transform: scale(1.08);
  box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.55), 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

.lightbox-btn:active,
.lightbox-close:active,
.modal-close-btn:active {
  transform: scale(0.96);
}

.lightbox-btn {
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 56px;
  height: 56px;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  transform-origin: 50% 50%;
}

.lightbox-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.08); }
.lightbox-btn:active { transform: translateY(-50%) scale(0.96); }

.lightbox-prev { left: 2rem; }
.lightbox-next { right: 2rem; }

.lightbox-close {
  top: 0.6rem;
  right: 0.6rem;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  z-index: 10;
}

.lightbox-vignette {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, transparent 62%, rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.4) 100%);
}

.lightbox-caption {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 1rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  text-align: center;
  z-index: 2;
}

.lightbox-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
}

.lightbox-counter {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* --- Footer --- */
.footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

.footer-content {
  max-width: 650px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.8rem;
}

.footer-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: #ffffff;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}

.footer strong {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.footer-sub {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  opacity: 0.65;
}

/* --- Scroll-to-top Floating Button --- */
.scroll-top {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 2.2rem;
  right: 2.2rem;
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.35);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
  opacity: 0;
  visibility: hidden;
  transform: translateY(12px);
  z-index: 99;
}

.scroll-top svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
}

.scroll-top.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  visibility: visible;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.scroll-top:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  background: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
}

/* --- Responsive Layout Adjustments --- */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .navbar { padding: 0 2rem; }
  .modal-wrapper { max-width: 90%; }
  .lore-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .nav-links {
    position: fixed;
    top: 76px;
    right: 0;
    height: calc(100vh - 76px);
    width: 280px;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.96);
    backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    padding: 3rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    transform: translateX(100%);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  }

  .nav-links.open {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  .nav-mobile-toggle {
    display: flex;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
  }
  .hero-stat-sep { height: 32px; }

  .modal { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .modal-header { height: 220px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
  .modal-profile-img { width: 80px; height: 80px; }
  .modal-champ-name { font-size: 2rem; }
  .modal-body { padding: 1.8rem 2rem; }

  .lightbox-container { width: 97vw; height: 88vh; }
  .lightbox-btn { width: 44px; height: 44px; font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .lightbox-prev { left: 0.4rem; }
  .lightbox-next { right: 0.4rem; }
  .lightbox-close { width: 38px; height: 38px; top: 0.8rem; right: 0.8rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .hero-stats {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-stat-sep { display: none; }
  .hero-stat { flex: 0 0 40%; }

  .controls { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
  .search-box { max-width: 100%; }

  .modal { padding: 0.6rem; }
  .modal-header { height: 180px; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; }
  .modal-profile-img { width: 64px; height: 64px; border-width: 2.5px; }
  .modal-champ-name { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .modal-champ-title { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .modal-body { padding: 1.2rem; }

  .tabs-header { gap: 1.2rem; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }
  .tabs-header::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab-btn { font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.6rem 0; }

  .ability-detail-card { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .ability-img-wrap { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
}

content.text:
/* ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
   RUNETERRA LEGENDS HUBS - ULTRA MODERN HEXTECH GLASS DESIGN SYSTEM
   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛ */

/* --- Variables & Core Palette --- */
:root {
  /* Hextech Gold Theme */
  --gold-dark: #785a28;
  --gold-medium: #c89b3c;
  --gold-light: #f0e6d2;
  --gold-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #785a28 0%, #c89b3c 50%, #f0e6d2 100%);

  /* Void / Cosmic Magic Dark Purple Palette */
  --bg-deep: #07040d;
  --bg-base: #0f0a1c;
  --bg-elevated: #161026;
  --bg-card: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.75);

  /* Accents & Status */
  --magic-blue: #00d2ff;
  --magic-cyan: #00bc8c;
  --magic-purple: #8e2de2;
  --error: #ff4e50;

  /* Borders & Glassmorphism */
  --border-light: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.2);
  --border-glow: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.45);
  --glass-bg: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4);
  --glass-blur: blur(14px);
  --shadow-glow: 0 0 12px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.5);
  --text-dim: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.78);
  --text-faint: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.48);

  /* Fonts */
  --font-heading: 'Cinzel', serif;
  --font-body: 'Inter', sans-serif;
  --font-ui: 'Rajdhani', sans-serif;

  /* Layout Depth */
  --z-bg: -3;
  --z-particles: -2;
  --z-nav: 100;
  --z-card: 10;
  --z-modal: 1000;
  --z-lightbox: 2000;
}

/* --- Resets & Base Styles --- */
*, *::before, *::after {
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  box-sizing: border-box;
}

html {
  height: 100%;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  font-size: 15px;
  background-color: var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-color: var(--gold-medium) var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}

body {
  min-height: 100vh;
  font-family: var(--font-body);
  color: #ffffff;
  /* Deep cosmic radial — violet core fading to pure void black, complemented
     by subtle gold/cobalt nebulae anchored to opposite corners. */
  background:
    radial-gradient(circle at 50% 20%, rgba(22, 16, 38, 1) 0%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 1) 100%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 25% 0%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.12) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 75% 90%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.08) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 90% 25%, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.06) 0%, transparent 50%);
  background-color: var(--bg-deep);
  line-height: 1.6;
  overflow-x: hidden;
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

::selection {
  background: var(--gold-medium);
  color: #000;
}

/* Floating Scrollbar */
::-webkit-scrollbar {
  width: 10px;
  height: 10px;
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-track {
  background: var(--bg-deep);
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb {
  background: var(--gold-dark);
  border-radius: 5px;
  border: 2px solid var(--bg-deep);
}
::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb:hover {
  background: var(--gold-medium);
}

/* Standard Premium Link */
a {
  color: inherit;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: color 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}
a:hover {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

img {
  display: block;
  max-width: 100%;
  height: auto;
}

button {
  font-family: inherit;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  color: inherit;
  cursor: pointer;
}

/* --- Particles Canvas & Deep Magic Backgrounds --- */
#particles {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  z-index: var(--z-particles);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.bg-gradient {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background: 
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 15% 15%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 85% 85%, rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.1) 0%, transparent 60%);
  z-index: var(--z-bg);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.bg-grid {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  background-image: 
    linear-gradient(rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.02) 1px, transparent 1px);
  background-size: 60px 60px;
  mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000000 40%, transparent 80%);
  -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, #000000 40%, transparent 80%);
  z-index: var(--z-bg);
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* --- Header / Navbar --- */
.navbar {
  position: fixed;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 76px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
  padding: 0 4rem;
  background: rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  z-index: var(--z-nav);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.navbar.scrolled {
  height: 64px;
  background: rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.9);
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

.nav-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.nav-logo-mark {
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  animation: logoGlow 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes logoGlow {
  from { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 2px rgba(200,155,60,0.3)); }
  to { filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px rgba(200,155,60,0.8)); }
}

.nav-links {
  display: flex;
  gap: 3rem;
}

.nav-links a {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  padding: 0.4rem 0;
  position: relative;
}

.nav-links a::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 50%;
  width: 0;
  height: 2px;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  transform: translateX(-50%);
}

.nav-links a:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

.nav-links a:hover::after,
.nav-links a.active::after {
  width: 100%;
}

.nav-mobile-toggle {
  display: none;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 6px;
  width: 30px;
  background: none;
  border: none;
  z-index: 101;
}

.nav-mobile-toggle span {
  display: block;
  height: 2px;
  width: 100%;
  background: var(--gold-light);
  border-radius: 2px;
  transition: 0.3s;
}

/* --- Hero Section --- */
.hero {
  position: relative;
  min-height: 100vh;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 8rem 2rem 4rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  /* Establish a stacking context so the splash sits above the global backgrounds,
     not behind the <html>/<body> gradient that was hiding it. */
  isolation: isolate;
}

.hero-splash {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 0;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center 25%;
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  /* Cinematic look: dreamy but visible — far less aggressively dimmed than before. */
  filter: brightness(0.62) saturate(1.05) contrast(1.05);
  transform: scale(1.12);
  opacity: 0;
  transition: opacity 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), transform 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  will-change: opacity, transform;
}

.hero-splash.loaded {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: scale(1);
  animation: slowZoom 60s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
}

@keyframes slowZoom {
  from { transform: scale(1.04) translate(-0.6%, -0.8%); }
  to   { transform: scale(1.12) translate(0.6%, -1.4%); }
}

/* Color grading washes drawn over the splash so the hero keeps the mystical
   gold/violet identity while still letting the champion art read through. */
.hero-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 0%,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.45) 40%,
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.72) 72%,
    var(--bg-deep) 100%);
}

/* Cinematic edges — darkens corners for a faux-darkroom vignette and focuses
   the eye on the center where the title lives. */
.hero-vignette {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 42%, transparent 0%, transparent 38%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 82%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.9) 100%),
    linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 0%, transparent 22%, transparent 78%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.55) 100%);
}

/* Subtle gold/violet light sweep drifting across the hero text area */
.hero-overlay::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background:
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 18% 22%, rgba(142, 45, 226, 0.18) 0%, transparent 55%),
    radial-gradient(ellipse at 82% 78%, rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.14) 0%, transparent 50%);
  mix-blend-mode: screen;
  pointer-events: none;
}

/* Floating "Featured Champion" credit in the lower-right corner */
.hero-credit {
  position: absolute;
  right: 2rem;
  bottom: 2rem;
  z-index: 2;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.78rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(8px);
  transition: opacity 1s ease 0.4s, transform 1s ease 0.4s;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  pointer-events: none;
  max-width: min(40ch, 60vw);
  text-align: right;
  line-height: 1.5;
}

.hero-credit::before {
  content: "✦";
  display: inline-block;
  margin-right: 0.5em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.hero-credit.visible {
  opacity: 0.78;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

@media (max-width: 640px) {
  .hero-credit { font-size: 0.68rem; right: 1rem; bottom: 1rem; }
}

.hero-content {
  max-width: 860px;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.hero-badge {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 100px;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.6);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  box-shadow: inset 0 0 10px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
}

.hero-badge-dot {
  width: 8px;
  height: 8px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: var(--magic-cyan);
  box-shadow: 0 0 10px var(--magic-cyan);
  animation: pulse 2s infinite;
}

@keyframes pulse {
  0% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
  50% { transform: scale(1.2); opacity: 1; box-shadow: 0 0 16px var(--magic-cyan); }
  100% { transform: scale(0.9); opacity: 0.6; }
}

.hero-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-weight: 900;
  font-size: clamp(2.8rem, 7.5vw, 5.5rem);
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  text-shadow: 0 10px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
}

.hero-title-line {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffffff 30%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
  -webkit-background-clip: text;
  background-clip: text;
  -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
}

.hero-title-amp {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  font-size: 0.48em;
  font-weight: 300;
  font-style: italic;
  margin: 0.4rem 0;
}

.hero-divider {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin: 2.2rem 0;
  width: 100%;
}

.hero-divider-line {
  flex: 1;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-light) 50%, transparent);
}

.hero-divider-mark {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  font-size: 1rem;
  text-shadow: var(--shadow-glow);
}

.hero-subtitle {
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  font-weight: 300;
  max-width: 620px;
  margin: 0 auto 3.5rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  line-height: 1.8;
}

.hero-cta {
  display: inline-flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 1rem;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-weight: 700;
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 1.2rem 3rem;
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-light);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  cursor: pointer;
}

.hero-cta:hover {
  transform: translateY(-4px);
  box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.45), 0 0 15px var(--gold-light);
  color: #000000;
  background: #ffffff;
}

.hero-cta-arrow {
  font-size: 1.3rem;
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.hero-cta:hover .hero-cta-arrow {
  transform: translateY(4px);
}

/* Hero Stats Bar */
.hero-stats {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 3.5rem;
  margin-top: 4.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 3.5rem;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.75);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
  border-radius: 12px;
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 1px 0 rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
  z-index: 2;
}

.hero-stat {
  text-align: center;
}

.hero-stat-num {
  display: block;
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  text-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
}

.hero-stat-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.12em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  margin-top: 0.2rem;
}

.hero-stat-sep {
  display: block;
  width: 1px;
  height: 44px;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent, var(--border-light) 50%, transparent);
}

/* Mouse Scroll Indicator */
.hero-scroll-hint {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 2rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  z-index: var(--scroll-hint-z);
}

.scroll-mouse {
  width: 24px;
  height: 38px;
  border: 1.5px solid var(--text-faint);
  border-radius: 20px;
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  padding-top: 6px;
}

.scroll-wheel {
  width: 4px;
  height: 8px;
  background: var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 4px;
  animation: scrollAnim 1.6s infinite ease-in-out;
}

@keyframes scrollAnim {
  0% { transform: translateY(0); opacity: 0; }
  50% { opacity: 1; }
  100% { transform: translateY(14px); opacity: 0; }
}

/* --- Section Title --- */
.section-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-align: center;
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

.section-title-line {
  display: block;
  width: 80px;
  height: 1px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--gold-medium) 50%, transparent);
}

/* --- Controls: Search & Filters --- */
.champions-header {
  margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
}

.controls {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1.2rem;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: center;
}

.search-box {
  position: relative;
  flex: 1;
  max-width: 320px;
  min-width: 260px;
}

.search-icon {
  position: absolute;
  left: 1.2rem;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 18px;
  height: 18px;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  pointer-events: none;
}

.search-box input {
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1rem 1rem 1rem 3.2rem;
  border-radius: 8px;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.8);
  color: #ffffff;
  font-size: 1rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.search-box input:focus {
  outline: none;
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
}

.search-box input::placeholder {
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* Pill tags filters */
.filter-tags {
  display: flex;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.filter-tag {
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.5);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-weight: 600;
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  padding: 0.6rem 1.4rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.filter-tag:hover {
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  color: #ffffff;
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.filter-tag.active {
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  border-color: var(--gold-light);
  font-weight: 700;
  box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.3);
}

.result-count {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-top: 1rem;
  min-height: 1.5em;
}

/* --- Champions Grid & Cards --- */
.champions-section {
  padding: 5rem 4rem;
  max-width: 1600px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}

.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: 2.5rem;
  padding: 1.5rem 0;
}

/* Cards (Vertical Loading Format) */
.card {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  height: 390px;
  cursor: pointer;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.card-img-wrapper {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  overflow: hidden;
  z-index: 1;
}

.card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1), filter 0.6s ease;
  filter: saturate(0.9) brightness(0.85);
}

.card-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.1) 0%, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4) 40%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.95) 100%);
  z-index: 2;
  transition: background 0.4s ease;
}

.card-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 3;
  margin-top: auto;
  padding: 2rem 1.6rem 1.6rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.card-role {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
}

.card-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  line-height: 1.1;
  letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: #ffffff;
  margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  text-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

.card-title {
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  text-shadow: 0 1px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8);
}

/* Interactive Card Footer Reveal */
.card-footer {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--magic-blue);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  margin-top: 1.2rem;
  opacity: 0;
  transform: translateY(10px);
  transition: all 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.card-footer-arrow {
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

/* Card hover triggers */
.card:hover {
  transform: translateY(-8px);
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 20px 45px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7), 0 0 20px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.25);
}

.card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.08);
  filter: saturate(1.2) brightness(1.05);
}

.card:hover .card-overlay {
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0) 0%, 
    rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.25) 30%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.98) 100%);
}

.card:hover .card-footer {
  opacity: 1;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.card:hover .card-footer-arrow {
  transform: translateX(5px);
}

/* --- Loader Spinner --- */
.loader {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.2rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}

.loader-spinner {
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  border: 3px solid rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.1);
  border-top: 3px solid var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 0.8s cubic-bezier(0.55, 0.055, 0.675, 0.19) infinite;
}

@keyframes spin {
  to { transform: rotate(360deg); }
}

.no-results {
  grid-column: 1 / -1;
  text-align: center;
  padding: 6rem 0;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
}

.no-results-icon {
  display: block;
  font-size: 3.5rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
}

/* --- Detailed Modal --- */
.modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: var(--z-modal);
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  padding: 2.5rem;
  animation: modalFadeIn 0.35s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalFadeIn {
  from { opacity: 0; }
  to { opacity: 1; }
}

.modal.fade-out {
  animation: modalFadeOut 0.25s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalFadeOut {
  from { opacity: 1; }
  to { opacity: 0; }
}

.modal-backdrop {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.9);
  backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(8px);
}

.modal-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 1140px;
  max-height: 90vh;
  background: var(--bg-elevated);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), inset 0 0 30px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.05);
  border-radius: 12px;
  overflow-y: auto;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  animation: modalSlideUp 0.45s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1) forwards;
}

@keyframes modalSlideUp {
  from { transform: translateY(30px) scale(0.97); }
  to { transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
}

/* Inner short load structure */
.modal-wrapper.min-load {
  max-width: 450px;
  height: auto;
  padding: 4rem;
}

/* Hextech close button — inherits all base styling from the shared
   .lightbox-btn/.lightbox-close/.modal-close-btn group below. */
.modal-close-btn {
  top: 1.5rem;
  right: 1.5rem;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
}

/* Panoramic Header (Perfect sizing) */
.modal-header {
  position: relative;
  height: 280px;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center 20%;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  padding: 2.5rem 3.5rem;
  overflow: hidden;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
}

.modal-header-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.2) 0%, 
    rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.6) 50%, 
    var(--bg-elevated) 100%);
  z-index: 1;
}

.modal-header-content {
  position: relative;
  z-index: 2;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 2rem;
  width: 100%;
}

.modal-profile-img {
  width: 100px;
  height: 100px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 3.5px solid var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 0 25px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
  background: var(--bg-deep);
}

.modal-header-meta {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
}

.modal-champ-name {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 2.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  text-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
  line-height: 1.1;
}

.modal-champ-title {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  font-style: italic;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: var(--gold-light);
  text-shadow: 0 2px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.8);
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.modal-diff-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
}

.meta-label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* Custom Stellar difficulty rating */
.difficulty-stars {
  position: relative;
  display: inline-block;
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  line-height: 1;
}

.difficulty-stars::before {
  content: "★★★★★";
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  clip-path: inset(0 calc(100% - (var(--diff) * 10%)) 0 0);
  -webkit-clip-path: inset(0 calc(100% - (var(--diff) * 10%)) 0 0);
}

.modal-badges {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.modal-tag-badge {
  background: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.15);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-medium);
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.75rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.1em;
  padding: 0.25rem 0.8rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

/* --- Tabs Layout --- */
.modal-body {
  padding: 2.5rem 3.5rem 3.5rem;
}

.tabs-container {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 2rem;
}

/* Premium Navigation header */
.tabs-header {
  display: flex;
  border-bottom: 1.5px solid var(--border-light);
  gap: 2.5rem;
}

.tab-btn {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.15rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  padding: 0.8rem 0;
  position: relative;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.tab-btn span {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.tab-btn:hover {
  color: #ffffff;
}

.tab-btn.active {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.tab-btn::after {
  content: "";
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -1.5px;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  height: 2.5px;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  transform: scaleX(0);
  transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.tab-btn.active::after {
  transform: scaleX(1);
}

/* Panel management */
.tab-panel {
  display: none;
  animation: panelIn 0.4s ease forwards;
}

.tab-panel.active {
  display: block;
}

@keyframes panelIn {
  from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); }
  to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
}

/* --- Lore Content --- */
.lore-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1.6fr 1fr;
  gap: 4rem;
}

.lore-text h2 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
}

.lore-text p {
  font-size: 1.1rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  text-align: justify;
}

.champion-sidebar-info {
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.8rem;
}

.champion-sidebar-info h3 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  padding-bottom: 0.6rem;
}

.stats-list {
  list-style: none;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.8rem;
}

.stats-list li {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  font-size: 0.95rem;
}

.stats-list li span {
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

.stats-list li strong {
  color: var(--gold-light);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
}

/* --- Combative Abilities --- */
.abilities-detail-grid {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  margin-top: 1.5rem;
}

.ability-detail-card {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.8rem;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.4);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  border-radius: 8px;
  padding: 1.5rem;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.ability-detail-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.4);
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.65);
}

.ability-img-wrap {
  position: relative;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: 64px;
  height: 64px;
}

.ability-img-wrap img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  border-radius: 6px;
  border: 2px solid var(--gold-dark);
}

.ability-letter {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: -6px;
  right: -6px;
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border: 1px solid var(--gold-medium);
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.ability-letter.passive {
  border-color: var(--magic-blue);
  color: var(--magic-blue);
}

.ability-desc-wrap {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.6rem;
  width: 100%;
}

.ability-desc-header {
  display: flex;
  justify-content: space-between;
  align-items: flex-start;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1rem;
}

.ability-desc-header h4 {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.25rem;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.ability-meta-tags {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.6rem;
}

.meta-tag {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.8rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  padding: 0.2rem 0.6rem;
  border-radius: 4px;
}

.meta-tag.cost {
  background: rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.12);
  border: 1px solid rgba(0, 210, 255, 0.3);
  color: var(--magic-blue);
}

.meta-tag.cd {
  background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
  color: var(--text-dim);
}

.ability-description-txt {
  font-size: 0.95rem;
  color: var(--text-dim);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.ability-tooltip {
  display: block;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--text-faint);
  margin-top: 0.5rem;
}

/* --- Skins Slider & Gallery (Uncropped / Clickable) --- */
.skins-tab-header {
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.skins-tab-header p {
  color: var(--text-faint);
  font-size: 1rem;
}

.modal-skins-container {
  display: flex;
  gap: 1.5rem;
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding-bottom: 1rem;
  scroll-behavior: smooth;
  scrollbar-color: var(--gold-medium) var(--bg-deep);
  scrollbar-width: thin;
}

/* Widescreen container for loading format portraits */
.modal-skin-card {
  flex: 0 0 auto;
  width: 200px;
  cursor: pointer;
  perspective: 1000px;
}

.modal-skin-card-inner {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 8px;
  overflow: hidden;
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  height: 360px;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
}

.modal-skin-card img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
  transition: transform 0.5s ease;
}

.modal-skin-card-title {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  width: 100%;
  padding: 1.5rem 1rem 1rem;
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(7, 4, 13, 0.95) 80%);
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  text-align: center;
  color: var(--text);
  z-index: 3;
}

/* Zoom overlay */
.modal-skin-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.7);
  opacity: 0;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  gap: 0.5rem;
  z-index: 2;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.zoom-icon {
  font-size: 1.8rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  transform: scale(0.8);
  transition: transform 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
}

.zoom-lbl {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 0.9rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--gold-light);
}

/* Hover skins */
.modal-skin-card:hover .modal-skin-card-inner {
  border-color: var(--gold-medium);
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.3);
  transform: translateY(-6px);
}

.modal-skin-card:hover img {
  transform: scale(1.05);
}

.modal-skin-card:hover .modal-skin-overlay {
  opacity: 1;
}

.modal-skin-card:hover .zoom-icon {
  transform: scale(1);
}

/* Skeletons */
.modal-skin-card.skeleton .modal-skin-card-inner {
  background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--bg-deep) 25%, var(--bg-elevated) 37%, var(--bg-deep) 63%);
  background-size: 400% 100%;
  animation: shimmer 1.4s infinite;
}

@keyframes shimmer {
  0% { background-position: 100% 0; }
  100% { background-position: -100% 0; }
}

/* --- Premium Widescreen Lightbox --- */
.lightbox-modal {
  position: fixed;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: var(--z-lightbox);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  animation: modalFadeIn 0.3s ease-out forwards;
}

.lightbox-overlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background: rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.96);
}

.lightbox-container {
  position: relative;
  width: 96vw;
  height: 92vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  z-index: 2;
}

.lightbox-image-wrapper {
  position: relative;
  flex: 1;
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  /* Leave breathing room at the bottom so the caption never overlaps the art */
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  overflow: visible;
  padding-bottom: 4rem;
}

.lightbox-img {
  /* Use the whole wrapper — LoL splash arts are ultra-wide (~16:7), so we
     let width and height both stretch up to viewport while keeping aspect. */
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  max-width: 100%;
  max-height: 100%;
  object-fit: contain; /* Absolutely NO crop, full original artwork preserved */
  border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.9);
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
}

.lightbox-loader {
  position: absolute;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  border: 3.5px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
  border-top-color: var(--gold-medium);
  border-radius: 50%;
  animation: spin 0.8s infinite linear;
}

/* Shared Hextech control button styling — lightbox & modal close */
.lightbox-btn,
.lightbox-close,
.modal-close-btn {
  position: absolute;
  display: grid;
  place-items: center;
  border-radius: 50%;
  background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.55);
  border: 1px solid var(--border-glow);
  color: var(--gold-light);
  backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: background 0.25s ease, color 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease,
              transform 0.25s ease, box-shadow 0.25s ease;
  box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.08);
  z-index: 10;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  line-height: 0;
  /* Critical: explicit transform-origin prevents baseline-shift bugs on hover in/out */
  transform-origin: 50% 50%;
}

.lightbox-btn svg,
.lightbox-close svg,
.modal-close-btn svg {
  width: 1.4em;
  height: 1.4em;
  display: block;
  margin: auto;
  /* Force exact pixel-perfect centering regardless of font metrics */
  position: relative;
  left: 50%;
  top: 50%;
  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
}

.lightbox-btn:hover,
.lightbox-close:hover,
.modal-close-btn:hover {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--gold-dark) 0%, var(--gold-medium) 60%, var(--gold-light) 100%);
  color: #07040d;
  border-color: var(--gold-light);
  transform: scale(1.08);
  box-shadow: 0 0 22px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.55), 0 10px 28px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6);
}

.lightbox-btn:active,
.lightbox-close:active,
.modal-close-btn:active {
  transform: scale(0.96);
}

.lightbox-btn {
  top: 50%;
  transform: translateY(-50%);
  width: 56px;
  height: 56px;
  font-size: 2.2rem;
  transform-origin: 50% 50%;
}

.lightbox-btn:hover { transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.08); }
.lightbox-btn:active { transform: translateY(-50%) scale(0.96); }

.lightbox-prev { left: 2rem; }
.lightbox-next { right: 2rem; }

.lightbox-close {
  top: 0.6rem;
  right: 0.6rem;
  width: 44px;
  height: 44px;
  font-size: 1.35rem;
  z-index: 10;
}

.lightbox-vignette {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  z-index: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
  background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 50%, transparent 62%, rgba(4, 2, 8, 0.4) 100%);
}

.lightbox-caption {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 1rem;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  text-align: center;
  z-index: 2;
}

.lightbox-title {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.6rem;
  color: var(--gold-medium);
  text-transform: uppercase;
  letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
  text-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
}

.lightbox-counter {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

/* --- Footer --- */
.footer {
  text-align: center;
  padding: 4rem 2rem;
  background: var(--bg-deep);
  border-top: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
  color: var(--text-faint);
}

.footer-content {
  max-width: 650px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 0.8rem;
}

.footer-logo {
  font-family: var(--font-heading);
  font-size: 1.5rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 0.15em;
  color: #ffffff;
  margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
}

.footer strong {
  color: var(--gold-medium);
}

.footer-sub {
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  opacity: 0.65;
}

/* --- Scroll-to-top Floating Button --- */
.scroll-top {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: 2.2rem;
  right: 2.2rem;
  width: 50px;
  height: 50px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
  background: var(--gold-gradient);
  color: var(--bg-deep);
  border-radius: 50%;
  box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(200, 155, 60, 0.35);
  cursor: pointer;
  transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
  opacity: 0;
  visibility: hidden;
  transform: translateY(12px);
  z-index: 99;
}

.scroll-top svg {
  width: 22px;
  height: 22px;
}

.scroll-top.visible {
  opacity: 1;
  visibility: visible;
  transform: translateY(0);
}

.scroll-top:hover {
  transform: translateY(-5px);
  background: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
}

/* --- Responsive Layout Adjustments --- */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
  .navbar { padding: 0 2rem; }
  .modal-wrapper { max-width: 90%; }
  .lore-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 2.5rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .nav-links {
    position: fixed;
    top: 76px;
    right: 0;
    height: calc(100vh - 76px);
    width: 280px;
    flex-direction: column;
    background: rgba(15, 10, 28, 0.96);
    backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter: var(--glass-blur);
    padding: 3rem;
    gap: 2rem;
    transform: translateX(100%);
    border-left: 1px solid var(--gold-dark);
    transition: transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(0.25, 0.8, 0.25, 1);
  }

  .nav-links.open {
    transform: translateX(0);
  }

  .nav-mobile-toggle {
    display: flex;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 1.2rem 2rem;
  }
  .hero-stat-sep { height: 32px; }

  .modal { padding: 1.5rem; }
  .modal-header { height: 220px; padding: 1.5rem 2rem; }
  .modal-profile-img { width: 80px; height: 80px; }
  .modal-champ-name { font-size: 2rem; }
  .modal-body { padding: 1.8rem 2rem; }

  .lightbox-container { width: 97vw; height: 88vh; }
  .lightbox-btn { width: 44px; height: 44px; font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .lightbox-prev { left: 0.4rem; }
  .lightbox-next { right: 0.4rem; }
  .lightbox-close { width: 38px; height: 38px; top: 0.8rem; right: 0.8rem; font-size: 1.1rem; }
}

@media (max-width: 480px) {
  .hero-stats {
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 1.2rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }
  .hero-stat-sep { display: none; }
  .hero-stat { flex: 0 0 40%; }

  .controls { flex-direction: column; align-items: stretch; }
  .search-box { max-width: 100%; }

  .modal { padding: 0.6rem; }
  .modal-header { height: 180px; padding: 1rem 1.2rem; }
  .modal-profile-img { width: 64px; height: 64px; border-width: 2.5px; }
  .modal-champ-name { font-size: 1.6rem; }
  .modal-champ-title { font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .modal-body { padding: 1.2rem; }

  .tabs-header { gap: 1.2rem; overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; }
  .tabs-header::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab-btn { font-size: 1rem; padding: 0.6rem 0; }

  .ability-detail-card { flex-direction: column; gap: 1rem; }
  .ability-img-wrap { width: 56px; height: 56px; }
}

